What I meant was

556
00:22:53,520 --> 00:22:54,320
you don't need it.

557
00:22:55,360 --> 00:22:57,200
On what grounds?

558
00:22:57,240 --> 00:22:58,400
Don't you have me?

559
00:23:00,600 --> 00:23:02,040
What if you abandon me?

560
00:23:02,280 --> 00:23:04,080
I won't have anything when the time comes.

561
00:23:04,480 --> 00:23:05,720
How is it possible?

562
00:23:06,600 --> 00:23:07,240
Impossible.

563
00:23:07,880 --> 00:23:09,040
It's mere words.

564
00:23:10,280 --> 00:23:11,520
Come on.

565
00:23:12,440 --> 00:23:13,520
I knew it.

566
00:23:13,660 --> 00:23:15,840
You're talking about the marriage certificate again.

567
00:23:17,240 --> 00:23:18,960
It's not that I won't marry you.

568
00:23:21,880 --> 00:23:23,320
We already made an agreement.

569
00:23:24,520 --> 00:23:25,880
Wait until I get the degree,

570
00:23:26,080 --> 00:23:27,160
find a job and buy a house,

571
00:23:27,160 --> 00:23:28,400
we will get married immediately.

572
00:23:29,120 --> 00:23:30,440
I have told my mother about it.

573
00:23:31,280 --> 00:23:32,600
She also agrees.

574
00:23:33,150 --> 00:23:33,800
Do you get it?

575
00:23:35,640 --> 00:23:37,400
So forget about your investment.

576
00:23:37,680 --> 00:23:38,960
Save that 300,000 RMB.

577
00:23:39,960 --> 00:23:40,600
Perhaps

578
00:23:40,720 --> 00:23:41,560
we can even

579
00:23:42,120 --> 00:23:43,240
buy the house earlier

580
00:23:43,240 --> 00:23:44,660
and marry ahead of schedule.

581
00:23:49,280 --> 00:23:50,040
Li Xiang.

582
00:23:50,640 --> 00:23:52,920
I never asked you to buy a house.

583
00:23:53,280 --> 00:23:55,680
You insisted that we won't marry until you buy a house.

584
00:23:55,680 --> 00:23:57,680
It's your business and you can take care of it.

585
00:23:58,050 --> 00:23:59,360
I will take care of my own money.

586
00:23:59,400 --> 00:24:00,760
Come on.

587
00:24:01,840 --> 00:24:03,360
You don't love me if you say that.

588
00:24:07,040 --> 00:24:08,800
I gave you ten years of my youth.

589
00:24:08,800 --> 00:24:10,240
Do you really think that I don't love you?

590
00:24:27,480 --> 00:24:29,440
We always argue a bit every time I come back.

591
00:24:30,920 --> 00:24:31,800
It's so disappointing.

592
00:24:34,440 --> 00:24:36,080
I'm not asking for your approval.

593
00:24:36,280 --> 00:24:37,480
I'm just informing you.

594
00:24:58,680 --> 00:24:59,520
I'm here.

595
00:24:59,520 --> 00:25:00,720
Are you at home?

596
00:25:00,920 --> 00:25:01,680
Yeah.

597
00:25:01,680 --> 00:25:04,200
After entering the courtyard, keep walking 
 until you reach the end.

598
00:25:04,200 --> 00:25:06,040
The wing on the right side is my place.

599
00:25:06,320 --> 00:25:07,040
Alright.

600
00:25:59,280 --> 00:26:01,040
Open the door, sister.

601
00:26:02,760 --> 00:26:04,360
It's late in the evening. Who is it?

602
00:26:11,600 --> 00:26:12,840
There's a ghost.

603
00:26:18,480 --> 00:26:19,560
What's the matter?

604
00:26:20,000 --> 00:26:20,680
Who is it?

605
00:26:30,280 --> 00:26:31,560
What was that?

606
00:26:31,560 --> 00:26:33,000
It scared me to death.

607
00:26:39,680 --> 00:26:41,320
That's my sister.

608
00:26:41,520 --> 00:26:43,000
Do you remember that I told you

609
00:26:43,000 --> 00:26:44,120
I have an elder sister

610
00:26:44,120 --> 00:26:45,720
who kicks anyone who scares her.

611
00:26:45,800 --> 00:26:47,640
You have such a bad memory.

612
00:26:48,440 --> 00:26:49,680
Why are you still laughing?

613
00:26:50,280 --> 00:26:51,880
I was almost scared to death by him.

614
00:26:51,880 --> 00:26:53,600
What kind of people are you bringing home?

615
00:26:54,360 --> 00:26:55,880
She scared me to death too.

616
00:26:56,120 --> 00:26:57,600
I thought I was in the wrong place.

617
00:26:58,120 --> 00:26:59,520
If the neighbors called the police,

618
00:26:59,520 --> 00:27:01,680
there would be nothing I can do to clear my name.

619
00:27:01,720 --> 00:27:02,680
You deserve it.

620
00:27:03,060 --> 00:27:05,560
Would it happen if you didn't think about the revenge?

621
00:27:06,040 --> 00:27:07,000
Also,

622
00:27:07,480 --> 00:27:08,920
it's okay if you were in the wrong place.

623
00:27:10,040 --> 00:27:10,960
When she opened the door,

624
00:27:10,960 --> 00:27:13,720
I saw a great beauty instead of you.

625
00:27:14,440 --> 00:27:15,560
If I didn't wear the mask,

626
00:27:15,560 --> 00:27:17,520
I probably could have chatted with her for a bit.

627
00:27:18,480 --> 00:27:19,360
Sure.

628
00:27:19,720 --> 00:27:21,520
Come over and chat with her.

629
00:27:22,400 --> 00:27:23,120
I'd rather not.

630
00:27:23,640 --> 00:27:26,200
What if your neighbors beat me?

631
00:27:28,640 --> 00:27:29,720
You've got a good sister.

632
00:27:29,720 --> 00:27:31,640
She certainly knows where the Achilles' heel is.

633
00:27:32,760 --> 00:27:33,720
Of course.

634
00:27:33,880 --> 00:27:35,200
You scared her first. You deserve it.

635
00:27:35,680 --> 00:27:36,840
I left the stuff at your door.

636
00:27:36,840 --> 00:27:37,640
Remember to get them.

637
00:27:39,080 --> 00:27:39,760
Oh no.

638
00:27:40,320 --> 00:27:40,920
My bag.

639
00:27:41,320 --> 00:27:42,280
I left the bag at your door.

640
00:27:44,680 --> 00:27:47,200
He finally remembered the bag.

641
00:27:48,280 --> 00:27:48,920
So what?

642
00:27:48,920 --> 00:27:50,520
Do you want to turn around and fetch it?

643
00:27:50,520 --> 00:27:51,440
No, thank you.

644
00:27:51,440 --> 00:27:52,980
I don't want to see your sister again.

645
00:27:52,980 --> 00:27:53,720
How about this?

646
00:27:53,920 --> 00:27:55,480
I'm going to the Art Studio tomorrow.

647
00:27:55,600 --> 00:27:56,640
It's close to your place.

648
00:27:56,800 --> 00:27:58,200
I'll come to you tomorrow and get it.

649
00:27:58,400 --> 00:28:00,000
How about I take it to you tomorrow?

650
00:28:00,000 --> 00:28:01,240
Alright? We'll be close anyways.

651
00:28:01,240 --> 00:28:01,880
What do you think?

652
00:28:04,080 --> 00:28:05,120
Ask him

653
00:28:05,520 --> 00:28:07,360
is he alright after I kicked him like that?

654
00:28:10,760 --> 00:28:12,280
My sister told me to ask you

655
00:28:13,200 --> 00:28:14,200
did she destroy your

656
00:28:14,480 --> 00:28:16,800
reproduction functions with that kick?

657
00:28:17,120 --> 00:28:17,720
It's possible.

658
00:28:18,040 --> 00:28:19,080
Let me tell you.

659
00:28:19,080 --> 00:28:20,720
If I can't have kids anymore,

660
00:28:20,880 --> 00:28:22,320
I will blackmail your sister.

661
00:28:22,920 --> 00:28:23,800
Sure.

662
00:28:23,800 --> 00:28:24,400
Welcome.

663
00:28:24,580 --> 00:28:25,840
If you become my brother-in-law,

664
00:28:25,840 --> 00:28:27,160
I totally approve of it.

665
00:28:54,280 --> 00:28:54,920
Good.

666
00:28:56,280 --> 00:28:58,440
That's all for today's rehearsal.

667
00:28:58,680 --> 00:28:59,800
See you tomorrow.

668
00:28:59,800 --> 00:29:01,560
See you.

669
00:29:01,920 --> 00:29:03,000
Goodbye.

670
00:29:03,800 --> 00:29:05,280
Bye-bye.

671
00:29:21,360 --> 00:29:22,880
The peach and the plum do not speak,

672
00:29:23,480 --> 00:29:25,720
yet a path is born beneath them.

673
00:29:26,720 --> 00:29:28,000
Hello.

674
00:29:28,000 --> 00:29:28,560
Hello.

675
00:29:28,880 --> 00:29:30,280
It's our second handshake.

676
00:29:31,120 --> 00:29:33,400
It's actually not the second time.

677
00:29:33,880 --> 00:29:35,320
I have met you many times.

678
00:29:35,320 --> 00:29:36,200
Really?

679
00:29:36,800 --> 00:29:38,560
It's just you didn't notice me.

680
00:29:39,920 --> 00:29:42,360
You sing so well.

681
00:29:42,960 --> 00:29:45,680
Your calligraphy is so beautiful.

682
00:29:46,520 --> 00:29:47,760
Thanks for the compliment.

683
00:29:48,360 --> 00:29:49,160
Let me take a photo.

684
00:29:49,280 --> 00:29:50,840
I didn't manage to take a photo last time.

685
00:29:50,890 --> 00:29:51,960
The characters evaporated.

686
00:29:52,640 --> 00:29:53,440
Alright.

687
00:30:14,080 --> 00:30:14,680
Can I help you?

688
00:30:14,680 --> 00:30:15,040
Hello.

689
00:30:15,040 --> 00:30:16,520
Can I ask if Liu Liangzhou is here?

690
00:30:22,200 --> 00:30:23,280
As for the sky,

691
00:30:23,440 --> 00:30:25,240
lower the brightness for a bit

692
00:30:26,240 --> 00:30:27,440
from here to there

693
00:30:27,960 --> 00:30:28,780
and apply a gradient.

694
00:30:30,160 --> 00:30:33,160
And the grass from here to there,

695
00:30:34,520 --> 00:30:35,800
less green.

696
00:30:36,680 --> 00:30:38,120
Lower the saturation level.

697
00:30:38,600 --> 00:30:39,160
Right.

698
00:30:40,120 --> 00:30:40,840
Lower.

699
00:30:43,800 --> 00:30:44,160
OK.

700
00:30:44,160 --> 00:30:45,000
The next one.

701
00:30:49,120 --> 00:30:50,080
And the shadow.

702
00:30:51,560 --> 00:30:52,280
Yeah. More shadow.

703
00:30:52,280 --> 00:30:53,080
A bit more.

704
00:30:54,200 --> 00:30:55,000
Over here.

705
00:30:58,120 --> 00:31:00,160
Make the highlight in this whole area brighter.

706
00:31:01,400 --> 00:31:02,080
Yeah.

707
00:31:02,080 --> 00:31:02,720
OK.

708
00:31:03,040 --> 00:31:03,680
The next one.

709
00:31:04,800 --> 00:31:05,920
Lower the saturation level.

710
00:31:06,400 --> 00:31:07,400
OK.

711
00:31:08,680 --> 00:31:09,200
That will do.

712
00:31:11,200 --> 00:31:12,000
Let's go.

713
00:31:12,760 --> 00:31:13,440
Come on.

714
00:31:16,040 --> 00:31:16,760
A bit more green.

715
00:31:19,520 --> 00:31:20,120
Yes.

716
00:31:22,160 --> 00:31:22,680
OK.

717
00:31:24,800 --> 00:31:25,480
The next one.

718
00:31:35,280 --> 00:31:36,600
Why did you leave?

719
00:31:37,160 --> 00:31:38,760
Because you were so absorbed,

720
00:31:38,760 --> 00:31:40,600
we didn't want to disturb you.

721
00:31:40,880 --> 00:31:42,560
I wanted to buy you dinner.

722
00:31:43,160 --> 00:31:44,200
Let's skip today.

723
00:31:44,280 --> 00:31:45,080
How about tomorrow?

724
00:31:45,080 --> 00:31:46,560
Shall we make the plan tomorrow?

725
00:31:46,920 --> 00:31:48,360
OK. Tomorrow it is.

726
00:31:48,560 --> 00:31:49,080
OK.

727
00:31:49,080 --> 00:31:49,800
Deal.

728
00:31:49,800 --> 00:31:50,640
Bye-bye.

729
00:31:56,960 --> 00:31:57,720
Sister,

730
00:31:58,920 --> 00:32:00,200
has it been

731
00:32:00,200 --> 00:32:01,480
a long time since you saw

732
00:32:01,480 --> 00:32:03,600
the back of a sturdy guy?

733
00:32:04,600 --> 00:32:05,520
What do you mean?

734
00:32:07,040 --> 00:32:09,160
I saw the way you looked at Liu Liangzhou just now.

735
00:32:09,380 --> 00:32:10,640
You couldn't take your eyes off him,

736
00:32:12,120 --> 00:32:13,840
Why are you bullshitting?

737
00:32:14,680 --> 00:32:15,800
I was half asleep.

738
00:32:15,920 --> 00:32:17,640
I look at all things the same way.

739
00:32:19,000 --> 00:32:20,520
What should we have for dinner?

740
00:32:21,160 --> 00:32:22,760
Chai Yong is receiving guests tonight.

741
00:32:22,760 --> 00:32:24,080
I have to attend that.

742
00:32:24,910 --> 00:32:26,840
Is it another business of hundreds of millions?

743
00:32:27,600 --> 00:32:29,680
Where can he get such a business?

744
00:32:30,760 --> 00:32:32,120
It's not about business today.

745
00:32:32,120 --> 00:32:34,200
Some of his friends from other places are visiting.

746
00:32:34,440 --> 00:32:35,360
It's just a dinner.

747
00:32:35,360 --> 00:32:37,000
Then why did he ask you to go?

748
00:32:37,640 --> 00:32:39,800
Tell me, why can't he do anything without you now?

749
00:32:40,060 --> 00:32:41,840
He is dependent on you. Textbook dependent.

750
00:32:41,840 --> 00:32:42,920
Shut up.

751
00:32:43,560 --> 00:32:44,880
Why does everything sound weird

752
00:32:44,880 --> 00:32:46,080
when you say it?

753
00:32:46,480 --> 00:32:48,160
Why don't you come with me?

754
00:32:48,600 --> 00:32:50,760
I'm not attending an old people's meeting.

755
00:32:51,440 --> 00:32:53,480
I wanted to bring you with me.

756
00:32:53,960 --> 00:32:56,160
Feng Xi asked us to go Karaoke tonight.

757
00:32:56,680 --> 00:32:57,600
Who is Feng Xi?

758
00:32:57,600 --> 00:32:59,120
She was the happy dumb girl next to me

759
00:32:59,200 --> 00:33:01,080
when I brought you to dinner last time.

760
00:33:01,080 --> 00:33:01,920
Do you remember?

761
00:33:01,920 --> 00:33:03,120
I see.

762
00:33:03,440 --> 00:33:04,520
Have fun.

763
00:33:07,720 --> 00:33:09,440
Well, I plan to go back home

764
00:33:09,440 --> 00:33:11,440
and read the script first.

765
00:33:11,440 --> 00:33:12,800
Where should I drop you off?

766
00:33:13,520 --> 00:33:15,240
Why are you so cunning?

767
00:33:15,520 --> 00:33:16,800
Can't you just drive me there?

768
00:33:17,240 --> 00:33:18,520
It's out of my way.

769
00:33:19,440 --> 00:33:21,680
When you want it, everywhere can be in your way.

770
00:33:21,680 --> 00:33:23,800
But the thing is, I don't want to do that.

771
00:33:25,200 --> 00:33:27,120
I'm falling in love with the sky, the earth

772
00:33:27,480 --> 00:33:28,800
and my destined love.

773
00:33:29,920 --> 00:33:32,280
I'm thinking about you, waiting for you

774
00:33:32,280 --> 00:33:33,680
and I can't focus my mind.

775
00:33:34,120 --> 00:33:35,120
What happens now?

776
00:33:35,120 --> 00:33:36,520
Did Li Xiang agree?

777
00:33:36,520 --> 00:33:37,840
His opinion doesn't matter.

778
00:33:37,840 --> 00:33:39,360
Anyways, I agree and that's it.

779
00:33:39,760 --> 00:33:42,400
I can't even bother to comment on the two of you.

780
00:33:43,840 --> 00:33:49,640
My destined love.

781
00:33:55,080 --> 00:33:58,120
Give me a round of applause.

782
00:33:58,400 --> 00:34:00,880
I love listening to you singing so much.

783
00:34:00,880 --> 00:34:01,880
It's pure happiness.

784
00:34:01,880 --> 00:34:02,960
How about I sing another song?

785
00:34:02,960 --> 00:34:04,440
You can even sing for the whole night.

786
00:34:04,560 --> 00:34:05,920
No problem.

787
00:34:06,040 --> 00:34:08,000
I'm called Mrs. Chinese playlist.

788
00:34:08,120 --> 00:34:09,440
Tonight, I will prove to you

789
00:34:09,480 --> 00:34:11,239
that I'm worthy of the nickname.

790
00:34:11,239 --> 00:34:12,280
Really?

791
00:34:12,280 --> 00:34:12,929
Of course.

792
00:34:12,929 --> 00:34:14,480
I'll request the song and you'll sing it.

793
00:34:14,480 --> 00:34:15,719
Request whichever song you like.

794
00:34:15,800 --> 00:34:16,760
Come on.

795
00:34:17,880 --> 00:34:19,480
Feng Xi just told me

796
00:34:19,480 --> 00:34:20,360
she likes you.

797
00:34:21,040 --> 00:34:22,320
I also like your personality.

798
00:34:22,320 --> 00:34:23,880
You're outgoing and cute.

799
00:34:23,880 --> 00:34:25,320
Alright, enough of the compliments.

800
00:34:25,560 --> 00:34:26,760
I know it.

801
00:34:27,520 --> 00:34:28,880
I have something serious to tell you.

802
00:34:29,600 --> 00:34:31,199
I plan to open a restaurant.

803
00:34:31,199 --> 00:34:32,449
Feng Xi is also a shareholder.

804
00:34:34,230 --> 00:34:34,920
How about that?

805
00:34:35,480 --> 00:34:36,480
Are you interested?

806
00:34:38,739 --> 00:34:40,280
Do you want to open a restaurant with me?

807
00:34:42,679 --> 00:34:43,880
Forget about it.

808
00:34:45,239 --> 00:34:46,760
If you don't like a company,

809
00:34:46,760 --> 00:34:47,560
tell me which one it is.

810
00:34:47,560 --> 00:34:49,679
I can try to put it out of business.

811
00:34:49,760 --> 00:34:51,960
You don't have to run it. We have Feng Xi.

812
00:34:51,960 --> 00:34:53,400
You just need to make an investment.

813
00:34:54,210 --> 00:34:56,120
I can't promise you how much money you can earn,

814
00:34:56,120 --> 00:34:58,280
but at least it's a long-term meal ticket.

815
00:34:58,280 --> 00:34:58,720
Wait.

816
00:34:58,720 --> 00:35:00,960
Really, Shan?

817
00:35:01,440 --> 00:35:02,920
Why do you choose me?

818
00:35:02,920 --> 00:35:04,680
There're so many rich business people around you.

819
00:35:04,680 --> 00:35:05,830
No matter which one you pick,

820
00:35:05,830 --> 00:35:07,000
all of them can cooperate with you.

821
00:35:07,000 --> 00:35:09,960
If they join in, it won't feel the same.

822
00:35:10,320 --> 00:35:11,800
I planned to do it myself

823
00:35:11,800 --> 00:35:13,560
and let Feng Xi run it.

824
00:35:13,560 --> 00:35:14,840
But after I told her about it,

825
00:35:14,840 --> 00:35:16,310
she wanted to be a shareholder.

826
00:35:16,800 --> 00:35:18,400
I thought it's actually good.

827
00:35:18,400 --> 00:35:20,000
If she invests in it, it's her business too.

828
00:35:20,000 --> 00:35:22,120
It's definitely different from working for others.

829
00:35:22,400 --> 00:35:23,720
In for a penny, in for a pound.

830
00:35:23,720 --> 00:35:25,360
So I decided to recruit people I like.

831
00:35:25,760 --> 00:35:26,720
That's why I came to you.

832
00:35:27,040 --> 00:35:27,520
Yeah.

833
00:35:27,520 --> 00:35:28,640
Let's do something together.

834
00:35:28,640 --> 00:35:29,640
It's so much fun.

835
00:35:33,880 --> 00:35:35,280
I think I'll pass.

836
00:35:35,980 --> 00:35:37,720
I'm used to following my own inclinations.

837
00:35:38,280 --> 00:35:40,040
I fear I would be a liability

838
00:35:40,040 --> 00:35:41,200
after I join you.

839
00:35:42,120 --> 00:35:42,640
Also,

840
00:35:42,640 --> 00:35:44,800
